--- What current step does this board actually make? ---
  MCP6004 Iq: 100 uA/amplifier x 12 amplifiers = 1.2 mA (near-constant)
  LM339 Iq  : ~0.8 mA quiescent + up to 3 x 1.3 mA of LED current
  STM32F030 : ~5 mA at 8 MHz
  SPI edges are the only fast transient, and they drive 6 CMOS inputs.
  -> a rail |Z| of a few hundred mOhm is entirely adequate here.
